Subject: [PATCH 015/127] arm: tegra: ktt30: enable HDA audio support for HDMI
 audio output

Signed-off-by: Mariusz Ptak <mariusz.ptak@kontron.pl>
Signed-off-by: Valentine Barshak <vbarshak@dev.rtsoft.ru>
---
 arch/arm/configs/ktt30_defconfig |   16 ++++++++++++++--
 1 files changed, 14 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/ktt30_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/ktt30_defconfig
index f37c4a3..aaad988 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/ktt30_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/ktt30_defconfig
@@ -304,9 +304,21 @@ CONFIG_BACKLIGHT_TEGRA_PWM=y
 CONFIG_LOGO=y
 CONFIG_SOUND=y
 CONFIG_SND=y
-CONFIG_SND_DYNAMIC_MINORS=y
 # CONFIG_SND_DRIVERS is not set
-# CONFIG_SND_PCI is not set
